      "name": "recipes",
      "description": "execute/list recipes already in system\nUse \"Stankins.Console [command] --help\" for more information about a command.\nSome fast usage\nSqlServer:\nSqlServer1)To export diagram :\nstankins.console execute -o ExportDBDiagramHtmlAndDot -a \"Server=..;Database=..;User Id=...;Password=...\" -a metadata.html\nSqlServer2)To export a table to excel:\nstankins.console execute -o ExportTableToExcelSql -a \"Server=..;Database=..;User Id=...;Password=...\" -a nameofTheTable -a nameofTheTable.xlsx\nSqlServer3)To export a table to csv:\nstankins.console execute -o ReceiveTableDatabaseSql -a \"Server=..;Database=..;User Id=...;Password=...\" -a nameofTheTable -o SenderAllTablesToFileCSV -a folderToSave\nSolution:\nSolution1)stankins.console execute - o ReceiverFromSolution - a path.to.the.sln",
